item.title: CVE-2023-21825|2024-08-02T09:51:51.096Z -- oracle%20corporation -- isupplier%20portal
item.description: Vulnerability in the Oracle iSupplier Portal product of Oracle E-Business Suite (component: Supplier Management). Supported versions that are affected are 12.2.6-12.2.8. Easily exploitable vulnerability allows unauthenticated attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise Oracle iSupplier Portal. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized read access to a subset of Oracle iSupplier Portal accessible data. CVSS 3.1 Base Score 5.3 (Confidentiality impacts). CVSS Vector: (CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:N/A:N).
